   <tp:treatment-sec sec-type="discussion">
      <p>
Remarks
</p>
      <p>
It is unclear why 
Otte (1994)
reinstated 
<tp:taxon-name>
N. marginatus
</tp:taxon-name>
as a valid species, even though earlier literature had already synonymised this species under 
<tp:taxon-name>
N. vittatus
</tp:taxon-name>
. Based on the observation of a female 
syntype
showing no difference with 
<tp:taxon-name>
N. vittatus
</tp:taxon-name>
, we synonymise 
<tp:taxon-name>
N. marginatus
</tp:taxon-name>
again under 
<tp:taxon-name>
N. vittatus
</tp:taxon-name>
.
</p>
